---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import tomImage from "../assets/images/site/Tom Photos/tom_portrait-guitar_01.jpg";
---

<Layout
    title="About Tom Durrant | Durrant Guitars"
    description="The story behind Durrant Guitars and the man who builds them."
>
    <div class="bg-background pt-32 pb-24">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div class="reveal">
                        <span
                            class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-400 mb-4 block border-l-2 border-white pl-3"
                            >The Builder</span
                        >
                        <h1
                            class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl text-white mb-6"
                        >
                            About Tom Durrant
                        </h1>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed reveal delay-100"
                    >
                        <p>
                            I didn't start building guitars because the world
                            needed another guitar brand. I started because I
                            needed an instrument that didn't exist yet—something
                            that possessed the unmistakable soul of a vintage
                            classic, but played with the precision and
                            reliability demanded by modern touring musicians.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Every Durrant custom is built entirely by hand in my
                            workshop. From the initial wood selection to the
                            final setup, I am the only person shaping the tone
                            of your instrument.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We don't do mass production. We don't do
                            compromises. The goal is simple: to build you a
                            guitar that makes you a better player the moment you
                            pick it up. A guitar that you will never want to put
                            down.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/10 reveal delay-200">
                        <a
                            href="/create-yours"
                            class="btn btn-outline uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold px-8 py-3"
                            >Let's build your next guitar</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative group reveal delay-300">
                    <div
                        class="absolute -inset-2 bg-gradient-to-tr from-white/5 to-transparent blur-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative bg-surface rounded-sm overflow-hidden aspect-[3/4]"
                    >
                        <Picture
                            src={tomImage}
                            alt="Tom Durrant in his workshop"
                            widths={[400, 600, 800]}
                            sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw"
                            formats={["avif", "webp"]}
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-105"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
